spec_data.Name: php-zendframework-zend-loader
spec_data.Description:
Zend\Loader provides different strategies for autoloading PHP classes.

You can include /usr/share/php/Zend/autoload.php from
your application to use the Zend Framework.

Documentation: https://zendframework.github.io/zend-loader/
